    ACCOUNT: "/assets/img/account.svg",
    HOME: "/assets/img/home.svg",
    TASK: "/assets/img/task.svg",
    SPACES: "/assets/img/spaces.svg",
    SETTINGS: "/assets/img/settings.svg",
    LOGOUT: "/assets/img/logout.svg",

    EXPAND: "/assets/img/expand.svg",
    PLUS: "/assets/img/plus.svg",
    EDIT: "/assets/img/edit.svg",
    CLEAR: "/assets/img/clear.svg",
}

export const SOCIAL_ASSETS = {
    VK: "/assets/social/vk.svg",
    GOOGLE: "/assets/social/google.svg",

    MAIL: "/assets/social/mail.svg",
}
